<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Blog Page üìù</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 900px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.8em;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #ffeb3b;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #f1f1f1;
    }

    .post {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: left;
      transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    }

    .post:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    }

    .post h2 {
      font-size: 1.6em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #ffe082;
    }

    .post p {
      font-size: 1.05em;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #fdfdfd;
    }

    a.btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee0979, #ff6a00);
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    a.btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6a00, #ee0979);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Animation */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Our Blog üìù</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Latest thoughts, tips, and updates from our team üí°</p>

    <div class="post">
      <h2>üå± Why We Love Fresh Fruits & Veggies</h2>
      <p>Eating fresh is not only healthy but also supports local farmers and the environment. We explore the benefits of going green and how you can start today!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="post">
      <h2>üöÄ Building with Express.js</h2>
      <p>Express makes backend development smooth and fun. Learn how we structure our apps and keep things simple using EJS and clean routing.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/product" class="btn">üõí Explore Our Products</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
